data.description: Do you need some country living but you want to stay close to town?! We have a great home for you. This property is located on the outskirts of Alexandria between Rapides Station and Airbase Rd. The home is placed on a 1.4 acre lot. There is a large, winding driveway that allows for plenty of parking for entertaining guests. There is a double garage and two storage rooms. The home has a lot of space with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, formal dining room, formal living room, den, and sunroom. There is a wood burning fireplace. There is a large courtyard off the back of the house that is the perfect hangout spot. This home is close to 3,000 heated sq ft and ready for its next owner. Ask agent about the current mortgage being assumable so you can keep the great interest rate! Schedule your showing today!
